      <title>万斯推迟前往瑞士就伊朗协议进行直接会谈的行程</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/18/us/politics/vance-delays-trip-to-switzerland-for-direct-talks-on-iran-deal.html</link>
